data.reddit:
16, female, 5'2", 101, white. duration: about 8 months, no meds

I don't really know how it started, and I'm not forcing it. It started soon before I got the flu in December. I didn't really want to eat, and even after it my appetite grew smaller. I got stomach flu in March, which also decreased how much I ate. 

For the past week I've hardly eaten anything. I had one fruit snack, a small bite of chicken and I believe that's all. I've tried eating the last few days, but once I put food in my mouth I almost puke. I've also tried eating things that settle lightly, but it was the same outcome.
